        <td width="500" align="center" class="resize">
        	<table width="500" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="resize">
            <tbody><tr>
            <td width="50%" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; color:#010101;" class="blockC"><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill2_211014.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill2_211014.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="400" border="0"></a>
            </td>
            <td width="50%" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; color:#010101; padding-top:20px; padding-bottom:20px;" class="blockL">
            	<p>NCS with The Challenge is an exciting youth and community programme which combines outdoor activities, skill development and community volunteering. This is a fantastic opportunity for talented, enthusiastic and experienced people wishing to work with young people and make a difference within their communities.</p>

<p>We have paid positions available for all entry levels, from those wishing to gain further experience in a youth work setting, to experienced Project Managers, Teachers and Youth Workers.</p>

<p>Please feel free to forward this email to anyone who might be interested!</p>
