        <td width="500" align="center" class="resize">
        	<table width="500" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="resize">
            <tbody><tr>
            <td width="100%" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:18px; line-height:22px; color:#010101; padding-top:20px;"><strong>LEADER AND MENTOR ROLES</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td width="100%" height="20" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="500" height="20" border="0" style="display:block;" class="resize100p"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td width="100%" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; color:#010101; padding-bottom:20px;">
            	<p>We have a number of diverse and challenging roles available on our seasonal programmes, from leadership and mentoring to skill-sharing and logistical roles.</p>

<p><strong>Leadership Roles</strong> (Semi-residential) Lead 60 young people and 15 staff members through a complex and demanding programme. Be responsible for managing challenging behaviour.</p>

<p><strong>Mentor Roles</strong> (Semi-residential) Facilitate, lead and pastorally care for your team, assisting in their personal development.</p>


            </tr>
            </tbody></table>
        </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody></table>
