            	<p><strong>When can you work on NCS with The Challenge?</strong></p>
<p>
<p>We run our seasonal youth programmes throughout the year. Find the best programme for you at <strong>www.ncsthechallenge.org/about-the-programme.</strong></p>

<p><strong>Spring:</strong> February to March</p>
<p><strong>Summer:</strong> Late June to Early October</p>
<p><strong>Autumn:</strong>Late October to Early December</p>
